            <abstract encodinganalog="520" label="Abstract">The Harding, J.L. mss., 1861-1864, are
                Civil War letters of John Lucas Harding, 1841-1865, who served in the Indiana
                infantry, Seventh Regiment, Company I, which fought first with the Army of Virginia
                and later with the Army of the Potomac.</abstract>
        </did>

